name: PS-17. MetaBall-Pseudorandom[25]
description: v4W.ENko - "PS-17. MetaBall-Pseudorandom[25]". The basic "PseudoRandom" is generating 25 vertices to continue the visual story about the "MetaBall Algorithm". The outlines are colored in the list of complementary colors depended on the sub-settings of the "metaball" charge centers.  "Pattern Standardization" series is upgraded with more complicated "MetaBall" structure and generating the form such as the "Abstract michro-scheme". The "links-lines" of the "metaball" charge centers  are generated with "Delaunay triangulation". Packed as GIF. 1024*1024px / 180 frames.
